summary:
In my working career travelling and event organising have always been a passion; a red ribbon that keeps coming back. Although trained as a teacher I enjoy working on projects and cultural -, business- and groupbuilding events. 

In these areas my previous work experience  and personal interests come together beautifully. I like to challenge myself and that is one reason why I have been succesful in my projects.
I am ready for a new challenge in Europe in a international company where my multilingual communication and organisational skills can be used to succesfully organise events or projects.

Feel free to contact me! I am looking forward to hear from you.
